data.title: 28 Later... with Jools Holland, BBC Television Centre, London, England, UK
data.text:
Notes

On Tuesday April 28th 2009, Depeche Mode performed two songs live on the 'Later Live... with Jools Holland' show, namely 'Wrong' and 'Personal Jesus'. On Friday May 1st, the full show was broadcast on the 'Later... with Jools Holland' show, in which two more performed songs were shown. Thus, Depeche Mode's appearance on the show was as follows:

28 April 2009:

Wrong

[Interview]

Personal Jesus

1 May 2009:

Wrong

[Interview]

Come Back

Walking In My Shoes

Sources

Source 1 is a 1080i HDTV capture of all four songs compiled from the two separate broadcasts, minus the interview.

Source 2 is the audio from the television broadcast by itself.
